{"tid":742176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殲15存缺陷或被放棄　俄專家：中國當年貪平所致","createTime":"2018-07-14T10:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T13:10:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"af268933182d8ded33c5875c221b4b72da73fc47","tid":742176,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T10:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/photo/bkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180714135403\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180714%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180714135403&h=14e36f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解放軍空軍副司令員張洪賀中將日前證實，中國正在研製新一代艦載戰機，以取代正在使用的殲15。同時，有傳殲15在技術上不夠完善，需要盡快更新換代，美國《國家利益》（The National Interest）雜誌甚至指殲15存在無法排除的缺陷。近日有俄羅斯軍事專家踢爆，問題源於中國當年為省成本，貪便宜向烏克蘭購買不能飛的蘇33原型機。 <br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯衞星通訊社引述軍事專家卡申（Vasily Kashin）稱，殲15之前的墜機，說明其存在諸多細微問題，這不足為奇。他表示，因為中國曾為節約成本，放棄購買俄羅斯蘇33戰機及其生產許可，轉而向烏克蘭低價買入用於測試的蘇33原型機T10K-7，再由中國工程師研發其改進版。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/photo/bkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001_02p.jpg?20180714135403\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180714%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180714135403&h=4cfdc64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殲15機師曹先建曾因墜機身受重傷，須留院治療419天。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/mobile/bkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180714%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001.html&d=Id4rIygsUOkloCAncYl3yVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=fb4b3b61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180714/mobile/bkncn-20180714132219388-0714_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"347f733e93ba25fbccfedfa0e95629876c2f9dbd","tid":742176,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTim